{"tid":2175422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何桂藍反駁警點名批評：若中共治下講真話有罪可拘捕我","createTime":"2020-08-26T12:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T14:17:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fd12f1511ac017d7ef0db8e72c6d4883720a736c","tid":2175422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/CAIB33TC5NBEJINZYUJAAB2N3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FCAIB33TC5NBEJINZYUJAAB2N3U%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=bdab8661\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FCAIB33TC5NBEJINZYUJAAB2N3U%2F&h=fc33e17e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/CAIB33TC5NBEJINZYUJAAB2N3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年7.21元朗站發生白衣人無差別襲擊市民事件，民主黨林卓廷到場了解情況卻被左報扭曲成「帶隊」搞事、雙方打鬥。警今晨更拘捕林等10多人，令市民深感震驚。而當日在現場採訪的時任《立場新聞》記者、有「立場姐姐」之稱的何桂藍更被白衣人連番襲擊受傷，何反駁警方指，事發當日下午已有襲擊事件，非任何人激化。而她當時只是如實直播現場實況，一刀不剪，相信市民可自行得出公正結論。她強調，作為記者及7.21受害人，有責任講出真相，如政權容不下真話，可儘管拘捕她。"},{"pid":"548c49326169d0b45e90584afb406f68787440ae","tid":2175422,"uid":343663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6c5dbb44a66f59541fc776619567c2bfe96d8b","tid":2175422,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6e30a3b7e107f4479e5fd3bbe7440832ba06c96","tid":2175422,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0706ad656c6785a4bb5270af2416c6fb8dd6a46d","tid":2175422,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"拉你咪拉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj